      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F7C014E8-23F7-4C03-91C4-A374E73FCDFB" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-5F4AA0FA-A234-483F-BAA2-7C4F64FEA446" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. MMID stands for Material ID and CPN stands for Customer Part Number
2.Derive MMID using CPN or In case MMID is received, that will be used for creation of the order</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-39A7702F-C1B2-4D76-A61E-3BCF98FED836" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E0965BF1-7E08-4158-A4D2-7052DEA12A11" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. No inventory check, credit check will be performed for Customer Contract</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-5963163B-BF0C-4B16-B2BD-825351E5B9F7" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. Call-off orders will be created referencing Customer Contract 
2. Call-off Order follow Standard Order process</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-FAD370C0-A305-4211-8400-C498F64666C8" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3A3F6449-C7EB-424A-8BAF-90E15F4D175D" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. Customer Contract have requirements for Products.
2. This is a quantity contract
3. Blanket PO will be recorded in a customer contract</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-C4BA9811-9769-4318-9D6D-DF6A7E370B1A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Determine ZCON Order Type</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0911988E-BFC4-487B-ADF3-71349FCF0E40" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#99CC00"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#99cc00" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#99cc00" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Processes are happening outside of Capture Order and are covered in subsequent L3s</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <group categoryValueRef="sid-659c6cc1-d6be-4ce0-a4c7-94dca04c7816" id="sid-CAFC35B9-3635-4281-9FD2-4C34ED0F2C0C">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
      </group>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-01B4C3B1-F992-4264-90F7-5B9C9BFEA474" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="true" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="18.0" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="true" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="18.0" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform Process Steward: Nuria, Galceran &lt;nuria.galceran@intel.com&gt;, and BPM Champion: Rebeca, Meza Redondo &lt;rebeca.meza.redondo@intel.com&gt; of any changes that occur within the flow from now onwards so that changes can be accurately reflected within BIC</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
